{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"instancetype","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"cameraLookingAtCenterCoordinate:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D","text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"centerCoordinate","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"acrossDistance:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@CLLocationDistance","text":"CLLocationDistance","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"distance","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"pitch:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@CGFloat","text":"CGFloat","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"pitch","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"heading:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@CLLocationDirection","text":"CLLocationDirection","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"heading","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"centerCoordinate","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The geographic coordinate on which the map should be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"centered."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"distance","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The straight-line distance from the viewpoint to the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapCamera\/centerCoordinate"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"pitch","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineCont